annotationA: Pre-mRNA-splicing factor Slu7; Participates in the second catalytic step of pre-mRNA splicing, when the free hydroxyl group of exon I attacks the 3'- splice site to generate spliced mRNA and the excised lariat intron
annotationB: DHX15 ortholog, isoform A; ATP binding; ATP-dependent helicase activity; ATP-dependent RNA helicase activity; nucleic acid binding; RNA helicase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: mRNA splicing, via spliceosome; neurogenesis
